snippet.title: Marsupilami Trailer 1996
snippet.description:
Marsupilami Trailer 1996

Official Content From Sega Of America

Disney characters, Marsupilami and his elephant pal, Bonelli, are on the run from a hunter, who wants to sell them to the circus. Great soundtrack adds to the fun.
Platforms: Sega Genesis
